    "section_double_6YBbxA": {
      "type": "section-double",
      "blocks": {
        "subheading_7HGMXU": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "subheading": "",
            "padding_bottom": 16
          }
        },
        "heading_EAcVPp": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "The City By the bay",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-x-large",
            "padding_bottom": 16,
            "heading_tag": "automatic"
          }
        },
        "text_mEJtMk": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Living here, you learn pretty quickly how to move with the city. The hills, the fog, the microclimates, nothing is flat or predictable. Whether you’re on a bike, a skateboard, or hopping on a cable car, you adjust as you go. After a while, the terrain starts to shape you. It changes your route, your pace, and how you move through the streets and into the hills.</p><p>That shared experience is where this collaboration comes from. Ferris interprets Chico’s relationship to movement through layered artwork that comes to life across a range of Ornot pieces. The City Collection reflects San Francisco as we know it, shaped by the people who move through it every day.</p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "padding_bottom": 16
          }
        },
        "buttons_HER6LC": {
          "type": "buttons",
          "settings": {
            "button_text": "Shop Collection",
            "button_url": "shopify://collections/city-collection",
            "button_type": "btn--primary",
            "button_size": "btn--small",
            "button_style": "btn--solid",
            "show_arrow": false,
            "padding_bottom": 16
          }
        }
